com.sun.mirror.apt

Interface Messager

  • Deprecated. 
    All components of this API have been superseded by the standardized annotation processing API. The replacement for the functionality of this interface is Messager.

    @Deprecated
public interface Messager
    A Messager provides the way for an annotation processor to report error messages, warnings, and other notices.
    Since:
    1.5
